    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional driver at an affordable price point. The engine and transmission are operational, though you may notice some minor vibrations at highway speeds and a few small fluid seeps typical for its age. The interior shows visible wear, including some fading on the upholstery and minor scratches on the dashboard plastics. On the exterior, there are several small dings and some paint thinning on the hood. It is a reliable 'point A to point B' car that is ready for the road but will likely require some routine maintenance and minor cosmetic TLC in the near future.",
