    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to drive home a fantastic vehicle that balances reliability and style! This car is in good condition, showing the care and attention it has received from consistent maintenance over the years. It drives smoothly, looks great, and is ready to provide many more miles of dependable service. It's the perfect choice for someone looking for a well-loved, high-quality ride!",
      "price": 34000.0,
